title: API keys
tags: [Improvement]
image: /images/changelog/api-keys.png
---

The API key, also known as a token, grants access to our API and allows you to integrate it into your continuous integration workflows.
Previously specific to a hub or documentation, we are evolving API keys so that they can now operate at the organization level and everything it contains.
This work is paving the way for significant upcoming changes, such as rights management, for example.